27
00:01:17,503 --> 00:01:24,568
[SPEAKER_15]: The city council has invited chief of staff, Nina Nazarian, finance director, Bob Dickinson, and the department heads of the departmental budgets listed above to attend this meeting.

28
00:01:25,069 --> 00:01:28,131
