33
00:01:47,968 --> 00:01:56,274
[SPEAKER_15]: And also folks if anyone wants to speak specifically on departmental budgets outside of the department heads if the public wants to speak you can just raise your hand on zoom, or come up to the podium.

34
00:01:57,154 --> 00:02:01,778
