00:23:12,751 --> 00:23:13,411
[SPEAKER_15]: Councilor Kerrio.

312
00:23:13,852 --> 00:23:14,752
[SPEAKER_20]: Thank you madam bill.

313
00:23:14,772 --> 00:23:19,113
[SPEAKER_20]: Thank you for your good words.

314
00:23:19,753 --> 00:23:20,273
[SPEAKER_20]: You're right.

315
00:23:20,293 --> 00:23:22,614
[SPEAKER_20]: You have increased the modernize the office.

316
00:23:22,634 --> 00:23:25,814
[SPEAKER_20]: It looks a lot more and more friendlier than it was before.

317
00:23:26,374 --> 00:23:35,436
[SPEAKER_20]: One of the things I've asked for in every budget, I did get it one year and then disappeared for another code enforcement person.

