[SPEAKER_01]: perhaps Health and Human Services.

379
00:28:42,932 --> 00:28:59,687
[SPEAKER_01]: And what that task force will do, it will be a non-public task force so that the public wouldn't be invited, but it would talk about specific enforcement cases where we have problem properties, where there's always problems, whether it be with crowds or whether it be with different things.

380
00:28:59,867 --> 00:29:06,713
[SPEAKER_01]: And that task force would get together and talk about what each department has for enforcement authority.

381
00:29:07,453 --> 00:29:12,014
