[SPEAKER_01]: for one year and it's 432 cases, which is good for two people.

471
00:35:38,168 --> 00:35:43,173
[SPEAKER_01]: I was doing in Newton by myself, I was doing 250 cases a year.

472
00:35:43,653 --> 00:35:46,055
[SPEAKER_01]: That's a busy year for a code enforcement officer.

