00:35:50,039 --> 00:35:59,241
[SPEAKER_01]: 455.

475
00:35:51,739 --> 00:35:59,241
[SPEAKER_01]: And I would say, judging by the resolve rate, I would say it's anywhere from 70 to 75% resolved.

476
00:35:59,601 --> 00:36:02,442
[SPEAKER_01]: So sometimes cases don't get resolved because they're ongoing.

477
00:36:02,882 --> 00:36:13,245
