00:37:57,728 --> 00:37:59,849
[SPEAKER_15]: Tim McGibbon, Commissioner of Public Works.

510
00:38:11,460 --> 00:38:25,126
[SPEAKER_26]: Just to give you an overview, and I know it's in your books, the DBW is made up of seven divisions, plus our admin, our clerks in the office, cemetery, and city hall office.

511
00:38:26,326 --> 00:38:32,268
[SPEAKER_26]: So the divisions are highway, engineering, water and sewer, parks, forestry, cemetery, and fleet.

