00:38:33,169 --> 00:38:35,910
[SPEAKER_26]: Today with me, I have a leader of highways, Steve Tanaglia,

513
00:38:36,390 --> 00:38:41,532
[SPEAKER_26]: leader of engineering, city engineer, Owen Wartella, and our tree warden, Aggie Tudin.

514
00:38:42,512 --> 00:38:47,493
[SPEAKER_26]: So if there are questions that kind of progress that we need answers from, they are here to help us.

515
00:38:47,513 --> 00:38:53,735
