519
00:39:08,161 --> 00:39:26,289
[SPEAKER_26]: And you may have noticed that our goals are really asset based and collaborative between division based, you know, since I've been the leader of the public works, I've seen a lot of opportunity for inter division collaboration, for example, highway and engineering.

520
00:39:26,929 --> 00:39:30,233
[SPEAKER_26]: engineering and water, forestry and highway.

521
00:39:30,693 --> 00:39:40,262
[SPEAKER_26]: So I'm really trying to, you know, cultivate that collaboration as much as I can to sort of continue to oil the machinery of DPW operations.

