526
00:40:03,916 --> 00:40:05,116
[SPEAKER_26]: So that's just an example.

527
00:40:05,176 --> 00:40:06,797
[SPEAKER_26]: So that's where our goals are focused.

528
00:40:08,502 --> 00:40:15,149
[SPEAKER_26]: And then I think, as you know, the DPW has two main funding sources, the General Fund as well as the Water and Sewer Enterprise Fund.

529
00:40:15,669 --> 00:40:20,774
[SPEAKER_26]: So the Water and Sewer Enterprise Fund has a different strategy associated with that just due to the nature of it.

530
00:40:21,515 --> 00:40:28,922
[SPEAKER_26]: So, you know, again, the focus is still on operations, but because of the asset management work we have done over the last couple of years,

531
00:40:29,923 --> 00:40:38,849
[SPEAKER_26]: We're beginning to look at the operations and how much work needs to happen over the, say, the next 10 years and how we can plan for that.

532
00:40:41,251 --> 00:40:45,733
[SPEAKER_26]: And also regulatory compliance is continuing to increase as time goes on.

533
00:40:45,813 --> 00:40:50,637
[SPEAKER_26]: So those are really what we're basing our goals off of.

