[SPEAKER_26]: It's about a million dollars.

584
00:44:23,584 --> 00:44:23,784
[SPEAKER_26]: Yeah.

585
00:44:23,864 --> 00:44:25,424
[SPEAKER_26]: We got a little bit more this year, wrap money.

586
00:44:25,484 --> 00:44:29,365
[SPEAKER_26]: We use that for some larger patching out there as well as some ceiling.

587
00:44:30,697 --> 00:44:38,599
