[SPEAKER_20]: Yeah.

597
00:45:27,803 --> 00:45:30,925
[SPEAKER_20]: Well, I mean, as far as snow and ice removal and things like that.

598
00:45:32,225 --> 00:45:35,427
[SPEAKER_20]: I think we only had really one storm this year.

599
00:45:35,707 --> 00:45:38,729
[SPEAKER_26]: Yeah, we did use a lot of salt, though, as well.

600
00:45:38,769 --> 00:45:43,871
[SPEAKER_26]: So I mean, we didn't spend as much on removals as other years, probably, yes.

601
00:45:45,732 --> 00:45:46,873
