00:48:33,215 --> 00:48:35,216
[SPEAKER_03]: We have that data from when that report was released.

646
00:48:35,376 --> 00:48:38,258
[SPEAKER_03]: Could we say, oh, so we're doing a million dollars better this year.

647
00:48:38,338 --> 00:48:40,419
[SPEAKER_03]: Just if we could have that number, that would be great.

648
00:48:44,241 --> 00:48:51,085
[SPEAKER_03]: Quickly on highway, in terms of curbing on these new projects, is it all granite curbing?

649
00:48:51,105 --> 00:48:54,166
[SPEAKER_03]: Has that issue gone away where we can now get granite curbing again?

650
