00:48:58,909 --> 00:48:59,129
[SPEAKER_03]: Great.

654
00:49:02,896 --> 00:49:10,797
[SPEAKER_03]: Can I go to trash next just feel free to just say yes or no on this seems to me that the increase in the trash contract this year is basically.

655
00:49:11,576 --> 00:49:14,298
[SPEAKER_03]: at least two-thirds of the total increase in the DPW budget.

656
00:49:15,079 --> 00:49:16,360
[SPEAKER_26]: Because it's a large item, yes.

