[SPEAKER_23]: you're always going back to your deferred maintenance as you're trying to keep ahead of the game.

1138
01:28:01,796 --> 01:28:07,684
[SPEAKER_23]: And it's, you know, just like Tim was saying, you keep going after that backlog, you keep going after that backlog.

