[SPEAKER_15]: Thank you so much.

3029
03:58:42,759 --> 03:58:45,321
[SPEAKER_15]: Thank you for bearing with us for four hours.

3030
03:58:45,381 --> 03:58:46,842
[SPEAKER_15]: Thank you.

3031
